---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Zapier to n8n Migration Services | LogicLoom Systems"
  description="Stop paying the 'Action Tax'. We migrate expensive Zapier setups to self-hosted n8n workflows."
>
    <section class="relative pt-40 pb-20 px-6 overflow-hidden z-10 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-8 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-orange-200 bg-orange-50/60 text-orange-700">
          <i class="ph ph-lightning-fill"></i>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Certified n8n Architects</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-[1.05]">
          Escape the <br /> <span class="text-[#FF6D5A]">"Zapier Tax."</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          We build enterprise-grade, self-hosted n8n nodes that handle millions of executions for a flat server fee. Stop paying per task.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
          <button @click="$dispatch('open-modal')" class="bg-slate-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all shadow-xl cursor-pointer">
              Calculate My Savings
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-white border-y border-gray-100">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-stretch">
            
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-10 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 opacity-60">
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-500">Legacy SaaS (Zapier)</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">The "Pay-Per-Breath" Model</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
                    <li class="flex gap-3"><i class="ph ph-x text-red-500 text-lg"></i> <span>Costs explode with volume ($1,500+/mo).</span></li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3"><i class="ph ph-x text-red-500 text-lg"></i> <span>Data lives on public servers (Privacy Risk).</span></li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3"><i class="ph ph-x text-red-500 text-lg"></i> <span>No access to file system or custom packages.</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-10 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-green-400">The LogicLoom Stack (n8n)</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Fixed-Cost Infrastructure</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-300">
                    <li class="flex gap-3"><i class="ph ph-check text-green-400 text-lg"></i> <span>Flat Server Fee (~$40/mo) for unlimited tasks.</span></li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3"><i class="ph ph-check text-green-400 text-lg"></i> <span>Self-Hosted: Data stays in your private cloud.</span></li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3"><i class="ph ph-check text-green-400 text-lg"></i> <span>Git Version Control & Full Python Support.</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-slate-900">The Migration Protocol</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
                <div class="p-6 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50">
                    <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-200 mb-4">01</div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Audit</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">We map every Zap, webhook, and filter in your current account.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50">
                    <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-200 mb-4">02</div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Re-Architect</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">We rebuild workflows in n8n, optimizing logic to reduce steps.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50">
                    <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-200 mb-4">03</div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Handover</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">We deploy to your server and hand you the admin keys.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-16">
                 <button @click="$dispatch('open-modal')" class="bg-[#0071E3] text-white text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-blue-600 transition-all shadow-xl active:scale-95 cursor-pointer">
                    Start Migration
                 </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>